\emph{Rachit}, the bravest of all Ortsa is camping on the ancient planet \emph{Earth}. On June 10, he decides to ride his motorbike along his latitude such that he would always see the sun on horizon. After a few hours, he gets bored and decides to ride along the longitude at the same speed as before. He notices that he can still keep up with the Sun for some time. Find the latitude. He is really intrigued by this and wants to do this with a star instead of the Sun. Find the condition on the co-ordinates of the stars for which this is possible. 